  "detailed_description": "This is a story about a girl saving her sister. Her sister Mu Deng has contracted a terrible \"Dreamless Syndrome.\" The beautiful researcher \"ZZ\" resolutely pilots an experimental machine to carry out the \"Dream Break\" mission—<br><br>Flying enemies continuously shoot bullets at you. You need to pilot the \"Dream Breaker\" to [graze bullets] and accumulate energy, then release the [Phantasm Skill] to clear the field at the right time. After clearing, the phantasm particles you collect can be used to upgrade your machine or change skins.<br><br>Scatter, Tunneling, Forcing, Reading... The backlash from memory projection causes her to mentally collapse. Who is the girl-shaped boss that appears deep in the dream?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/d58db7e2ff868ef909e105610918e646.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/122a5bacd2df71de13d723c41498ea8f.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=650 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/122a5bacd2df71de13d723c41498ea8f.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Step into the school life of the silent middle schooler \"Mu Deng,\" after encounters, bullying, and betrayal, what follows is despair, or perhaps...?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/2635bfdf6bbca1814e940583cb152a2e.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=86 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/慕灯动态图-EN.gif?t=1769181852\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c866a7783a78d051e0094afe80bc2542.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/6a11624c812555967a8e33f0c4506eff.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/6a11624c812555967a8e33f0c4506eff.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/6a11624c812555967a8e33f0c4506eff.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c866a7783a78d051e0094afe80bc2542.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c61aacace899a510bf8dfc2e85901026.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c61aacace899a510bf8dfc2e85901026.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c61aacace899a510bf8dfc2e85901026.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game offers four playable characters. Players can choose \"Naoko\" with the [OT-A09], \"Mu Deng\" with the [OT-A09-MK2], the \"Plague Nun\" with the [OT-A10], or the mysterious \"Girl\" to infiltrate dreams and complete missions. Each machine has different bullet characteristics and skill styles.<br><br><strong>By the way, you can also change machine skins to fight in the fantasy image of female characters.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/349707f778c83070ed01b990659fc400.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/ab693a746ef979bfbeab22d89de10add.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/ab693a746ef979bfbeab22d89de10add.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/ab693a746ef979bfbeab22d89de10add.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c866a7783a78d051e0094afe80bc2542.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/d35000af60ed7b2662a60a7405bd7d19.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/d35000af60ed7b2662a60a7405bd7d19.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/d35000af60ed7b2662a60a7405bd7d19.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/370b38e3bf5d81dc18761a837c